  ;; ========================================================================
  ;; TFLN PHOTONIC INTEGRATED CIRCUIT (U3)
  ;; ========================================================================
  ;; Module: Custom edge-coupler, 25x8mm
  ;; 8x TX RF drive inputs (from NCE SerDes, 100Ω differential, AC-coupled via C10)
  ;; 8x RX photodetector monitor outputs (analog → U21 ADC)
  ;; 8x DC bias inputs (from U24 DAC)
  ;; TEC thermal control interface
  ;; MPO-24 fiber connector (J11) at board edge
  ;; ========================================================================

